metadata.name: PH/AI#1
metadata.description:
PHYSICAL ART + VIRTUAL REALITY
Original collection created from a physical work that mixes acrylic technique, virtual reality and digital. Digital manipulation until it presents an organic work of art that is good to appreciate. It is not just about distorting elements or shapes. The eye evaluates the work, part done by hand, the other part by a robot.
